2021年1月，美国[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]参议员、前总统候选人[[伯尼·桑德斯|伯尼·桑德斯]]戴着独特的手套坐在[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]的[[2021年美国总统就职典礼|就职典礼]]上的一张照片在网上疯传。这张照片在网络上走红，引发了一些版本的修改，把桑德斯放在了历史照片和其他幽默的背景中。迷因的流行导致了桑德斯的知名度和对手套的需求的增加。
== 背景 ==
2021年1月20日，在乔·拜登的就职典礼上，一组佛蒙特州参议员、前总统候选人伯尼·桑德斯的照片由法新社摄影师布兰登·斯迈洛斯基拍摄。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-01-26 |title=Photographer who took Bernie Sanders mittens snap says shot is 'not that nice': 'I'm not going to put it in a portfolio' |work=The Independent |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/art/news/bernie-sanders-mittens-photographer-inauguration-b1792328.html |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128012151/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/art/news/bernie-sanders-mittens-photographer-inauguration-b1792328.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>照片上桑德斯戴着口罩坐在椅子上，穿着冬衣，最引人注目的是他戴着一副又大又蓬松的手套，这副手套是佛蒙特州小学老师珍·埃利斯制作的。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-01-21 |title=Bernie Sanders spawns splash of memes with inaugural attire |work=Associated Press |url=https://apnews.com/article/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-meme-56c450c768447cd374f86e12fd907a9a |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128105926/https://apnews.com/article/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-meme-56c450c768447cd374f86e12fd907a9a |dead-url=no }}</ref>这张照片在网络上成为了一个迷因。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Cooper |first=Gael |title=Bernie Sanders' inauguration mittens meme: The funniest versions |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-the-funniest-versions-of-the-meme/ |access-date=2021-01-24 |website=CNET |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123194822/https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-the-funniest-versions-of-the-meme/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The mittens that resonated around the world |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/22/bernie-sanders-meme-inauguration/ |access-date=2021-01-24 |website=Washington Post |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123192718/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/22/bernie-sanders-meme-inauguration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Martin Belam |date=2021-01-21 |title='You just can't get everything you want': Bernie Sanders' mittens not for sale |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/21/bernie-sanders-mittens-not-for-sale |access-date=2021-01-24 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123180837/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/21/bernie-sanders-mittens-not-for-sale |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 迷因和商品 ==
这张照片被编辑和修改了许多版本，其中桑德斯被放置在各种流行的和历史的照片中，以一种类似于[[世贸中心上的游客|世贸中心上的游客]]这种迷因使用的方式，<ref>{{Cite web |last=Kipling |first=Ella |title=How To Put Bernie In A Picture |url=https://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2021/01/21/how-to-put-bernie-in-a-picture-sanders-meme-goes-viral-after-inauguration-photo/ |access-date=2021-01-24 |website=HITC |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125105205/https://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2021/01/21/how-to-put-bernie-in-a-picture-sanders-meme-goes-viral-after-inauguration-photo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>包括[[蝙蝠侠|蝙蝠侠]]、[[星际迷航|星际迷航]]和韦恩的世界。同时建立了一个网站，让桑德斯的照片可以放到[[谷歌街景|谷歌街景]]照片中。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-01-24 |title=Bernie Sanders' inauguration mittens meme won't quit: The funniest versions |work=C-Net |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-meme-wont-quit-the-funniest-versions/ |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130140656/https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens-meme-wont-quit-the-funniest-versions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>随后，这张照片被用于生产大量商品，其中包括盘子，T恤，贴纸和酒杯。<ref name="nbc">{{Cite news |date=2021-01-28 |title=10 funny gifts inspired by the Bernie Sanders mittens meme |work=NBC News |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/shopping/gift-guides/bernie-mittens-meme-gifts-n1256020 |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129233835/https://www.nbcnews.com/shopping/gift-guides/bernie-mittens-meme-gifts-n1256020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>桑德斯对这个表情包及其各种衍生品的反应很好，<ref>{{Cite web |last=Reilly |first=Nick |title=Yes, Bernie Sanders has seen all of your inauguration memes |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/yes-bernie-sanders-has-seen-all-of-your-inauguration-memes-2862727 |access-date=2021-01-24 |website=NME |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122161911/https://www.nme.com/news/music/yes-bernie-sanders-has-seen-all-of-your-inauguration-memes-2862727 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他决定卖掉印有这张照片的运动衫，为慈善事业筹集资金，<ref>{{Cite web |last=Ritschel |first=Chelsea |title=Bernie Sanders is selling inaugeration meme sweatshirts for charity |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/bernie-sanders-meme-sweatshirt-inauguration-b1791477.html |access-date=2021-01-24 |website=The Independent |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123204938/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/bernie-sanders-meme-sweatshirt-inauguration-b1791477.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>该活动的收益至少为180万美元。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Rathke |first=Lisa |date=2021-01-28 |title=Bernie Sanders' mittens, memes help raise $1.8M for charity |work=Associated Press |url=https://apnews.com/article/bernie-sanders-mittens-memes-charity-3f8afd8e8a5a0b8b9709dd6d4d30ec13 |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128233102/https://apnews.com/article/bernie-sanders-mittens-memes-charity-3f8afd8e8a5a0b8b9709dd6d4d30ec13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

因为这个迷因，埃利斯收到了成千上万的请求，很多人都想要这双手套。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news |date=2021-01-27 |title=Meet the woman behind Bernie Sanders' famous mittens |work=BBC News |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/world-55818859 |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129003800/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/world-55818859 |dead-url=no }}</ref>尽管她已经不再定期制作手套，但她还是利用公众的关注制作了三双手套，用于慈善机构和女儿的大学基金拍卖。<ref name=":0" />埃利斯与织布硬袜公司合作，生产了一系列与手套图案相同的袜子，其收益将捐给佛蒙特州的食品银行。<ref name=nbc/><ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-01-27 |title=Bernie Sanders' mitten creator is making socks inspired by the famous meme |work=C-NET |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-mitten-creator-is-making-socks-inspired-by-the-famous-meme/ |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129190753/https://www.cnet.com/news/bernie-sanders-mitten-creator-is-making-socks-inspired-by-the-famous-meme/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>编织作家凯特·阿瑟利很欢迎人们对这款迷因手套的兴趣，并在《卫报》的一篇文章中详细介绍了如何制作一款类似的手套。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-01-25 |title=How to make Bernie Sanders' inauguration mittens |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2021/jan/25/how-to-make-bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129185619/https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2021/jan/25/how-to-make-bernie-sanders-inauguration-mittens |dead-url=no }}</ref>桑德斯穿的伯顿滑雪板夹克也越来越受欢迎，导致该公司向伯灵顿儿童和家庭部捐赠了其中的50件。<ref name=nbc/>

